high_descs: Move to the table just ahead
Pick up the knife from the table
Turn around and go to the stove behind and to the left
Put the knife in the small pan at the back of the stove
Pick up the small pan with the knife sticking up from it
Turn left and go straight to the table
Place the pan with the knife above the left most spoon
anns.task_desc: Placing a pan with a knife on a table

high_descs: Move around the table towards the white refrigerator then turn left and face the table.
Pick up the golden handled knife to the left of the spoon from the center of the table.
Turn right and move towards the white trash bag on the other side of the room then turn left and move to the range.
Place the knife in the pan on the range's back right burner.
Pick up the pan containing the knife from the range's back right burner.
Turn left, move towards the white safe in the corner to the left of the black garbage bin, then turn left and face the table.
Place the bowl containing the knife on the table to the rear of the spoon to the right of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan containing a knife on the table.

high_descs: Go to the round, black table in front of you.
Pick up the knife in front of the plant and spoons.
Turn to your right and walk to the center of the kitchen, then turn to your left and go to the stove.
Place the knife in the pan on the front, right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan on the front right burner of the stove, with the knife inside it.
Turn to your left and walk back to the black round table.
Place the pan, with the knife inside it, on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a knife on the table.

high_descs: Go to the right side of the table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn around and walk left to the stove.
Put the knife on the plate.
Pick up the plate.
Turn left and walk straight to the right side of the table and face it.
Put the plate on the table to the left of the potted plant.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a knife on it on a table.

high_descs: Go to the right and directly left to stay at the round table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Place the knife above the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan, and keep the knife as well.
Turn to the left and go back to the circle table.
Place the pan and knife on the circle table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan from the stove to the table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk a little bit, and then turn around and walk back to the table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around, walk straight, and then turn left towards the stove.
Place the knife on the plate behind the pan.
Pick up the plate with the knife from the stove.
Turn left, walk towards the table on the left.
Place the plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the knife on the plate to put it on the table.
